rComments: Really good teacher made a subject I had no interest in fun and thought provoking. Open minded fair marker. He's pretty funny and a little scatter brained. Plus he is absolutely adorable.

Very enthusiastic and very clear. Determined to help everybody understand. Also funny in a scatter-brained sort of way. Liked him a lot - he made the class a lot more thought-provoking than it could have been.
Seemed pretty confident in knowing what he was teaching. Always willing to help clarify stuff after class, but was a pretty hard marker. Overall he was decent.
